Two Dimensional Array:- Two Dimensional array has two sub script one for the row and another for the column which forms a matrix.

How to Declare :
data_type[][] array_name = new data_type[row_size][col_size];
E.g.
int[][] arr = new int[3][2];

Initilazation of Matrix :
int[][] arr = {
                1,2,
                3,4
            }


